The '''Wehttam''' were the inhabitants of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Wehttam]].<ref name="BTS 14">''[[Before the Storm]]'', Chapter 14.</ref> They spoke the language known as [[Wehttam (language)|Wehttam]].<ref name="SOL 1">''[[Shield of Lies]]'', Chapter 1.</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Although the planet Wehttam plays a significant role in the ''[[Black Fleet Crisis]]'' series of novels, only ''[[Before the Storm]]'' mentions a group known as "the Wehttam." The context leaves unclear whether the term refers to a [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Species/Legends|species]] native to Wehttam or simply acts as a demonym for the inhabitants of the world. Wehttam is Matthew backwards.

